  <section>
    <p>ComptoxAI is a toolkit designed to enable AI and data science research in computational toxicology. Like many disciplines in biomedicine, computational toxicology is experiencing a deluge of valuable data being generated in a wide array of modalities and levels of application. However, the tools for interacting with these data are - at best - inconsistent, outdated, and fail to leverage state-of-the-art computational methods. We intend for ComptoxAI to change this.</p>
